# 🐾 Pet Adoption API (Node.js + Express)

A simple REST API for managing adoptable pets using **Node.js** and **Express.js**. Built to demonstrate route modularization using `express.Router()`, with basic data validation and dynamic routing.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Modular route handling with `express.Router()`
- ✅ List all available pets
- ✅ Search for pets by name (case-insensitive)
- ✅ Add new pets with input validation
- ✅ Returns appropriate error codes (400, 404)

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- Postman / Thunder Client (for testing)
- In-memory data (MongoDB integration coming soon)

---


